name: Podracer Collision
Lore: 'Podracing demands constant attention to many variables as well as all opponents. Failure to do so can often result in reduced performance.',
Text: 'USED: If you just verified opponent''s Reserve Deck, search that Reserve Deck and place one Interrupt found there out of play.LOST: Lose 1 Force to remove a race destiny (random selection) from any Podracer and place it in owner''s hand.',
